;;-&gt; nil</p>

<p>(-main)
;;-&gt; nil
```</p>

<p>Or just run this from the same directory as the script:</p>

<p><code>bash
java -cp .:/path/to/clojure.jar clojure.main -m sierpinski sierpinski.clj
</code></p>

